DESCRIPTION:The Duke/UNC Latin American Working Group's mini-conference is
  happening on Friday\, April 10 from 11:00 am until 3:45 pm at Gross Hall
  (Room 230E).\n\nThis year\, we invited Prof. Yann P. Kerevel (Louisiana 
 State University) and Frederico Batista (UNC Charlotte). Isabella Randle 
 (UNC) and Rodrigo Mahlmeister will be our graduate student presenters.\n\
 nLunch will be provided for attendees. Please complete this survey if you
  plan to attend the event and join us for lunch.\n\nhttps://unc.az1.qualt
 rics.com/jfe/form/SV_2o4ZybIYcQuUA1E
