 r ESPN\nKEVIN WHITE - Renowned former athletic director at Duke\, Notre D
 ame\, Arizona State\, Tulane\, Maine\, and Loras College\nDORIANE LAMBELE
 T COLEMAN - Thomas L. Perkins Distinguished Professor Law\, Chair of Duke
 's Athletic Council\, Co-Director of Duke's Center for Sports Law and Pol
